	    "values" : [ "Keep-Alive" ]
	  }, {
	    "name" : "User-Agent",
	    "values" : [ "Apache-HttpClient/4.5.2 (Java/1.8.0_91)" ]
	  }, {
	    "name" : "Accept-Encoding",
	    "values" : [ "gzip,deflate" ]
	  }, {
	    "name" : "Content-Length",
	    "values" : [ "28" ]
	  } ],
	  "keepAlive" : true,
	  "secure" : false,
	  "body" : "{ \"name\":\"Chuck\", \"age\":56 }"
	}

 did not match expectation:

	{
	  "method" : "PUT",
	  "path" : "/foo",
	  "headers" : [ {
	    "name" : "Content-Type",
	    "values" : [ "text/plain" ]
	  } ],
	  "body" : "Something Interesting"
	}

 because:

	method matches = true
	path matches = true
	query string parameters match = true
	body matches = false
	headers match = false
	cookies match = true
	keep-alive matches = true
	ssl matches = true
